items.badge_description: Want to enjoy a day of brews, but need to keep your wits sharp? There are plenty of delicious brews under 5% for you to sip on throughout the day. That's 340 different beers with an ABV of 5% and lower.

What happens when you take two or more amazing breweries, throw them into the tank and let them ferment together? An amazing collaboration beer, that’s what! Cheers to working together to create the perfect flavor. That's 20 different beers that have been brewed as a collaboration. Try 5 more for Level 5!
It takes the perfect amount of light, the right framing and a touch of creative love to get the perfect picture of your brew. Now it’s time to drink it! That’s 5 check-ins with a photo.

Round and round the wheel goes! Which style you’ll be drinking, nobody knows! Your desire to explore different styles is inspiring. Keep it up! That's a check-in to at least 130 different styles. Try 5 more for Level 27!
Ahh, the trusty pale ale; crisp, refreshing, and always a good choice in a bind. That's 150 different Pale Ales or American Pale Wheats. Try 5 more for Level 31.
